# get_irida_analysis_status
# get the state of an analysis submission
# PROJECT_ID is used only for tab completion, not passed to the API
# ANALYSIS_ID is the actual argument used in the curl call
#
# NOTE: tab completion shows all analysis submissions regardless of state.
# Only completed analyses with output will return results from get_irida_analysis_results.
#
# example: get_irida_analysis_status [TAB for project id] 13:Slush [TAB for analysis id] 42215:Assembly_QC__2-3-2025
